Definition: any of various water-soluble compounds capable of turning litmus blue and reacting with an acid to form a salt and water
Example: bases include oxides and hydroxides of metals and ammonia
Synonyms: verb, consumption, change, basify, alkali, alkalize, alkalify, compound, any, of, various, water-soluble, compounds, capable, turning, litmus, blue, and, reacting, with, an, acid, to, form, a, salt, water, bases, include, oxides, hydroxides, metals, ammonia
Category: noun.substance
